title: Multani Mitti Soap
description: Pamper your skin with the goodness of nature with our artisanal Multani Mitti soap bar, carefully handcrafted by skilled artisans. Infused with the natural goodness of Multani Mitti (Fuller's Earth), this soap bar gently cleanses and detoxifies your skin, leaving it feeling refreshed and rejuvenated. Known for its deep cleansing and oil-absorbing properties, Multani Mitti helps unclog pores and remove impurities, giving you clear and glowing skin. Indulge in the luxurious lather and earthy fragrance of our Multani Mitti soap bar for a spa-like bathing experience every day.
